<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <%view head%>
    <body>
        <main>
            <%view mainheader%>
            <div class="mw-100 d-flex flex-both align-items-center justify-content-center flex-column">

                <!-- Web Development -->
                <div class="main-text-container container">
                    <h1 class="mokoto main-text title">Web Development</span></h1>
                    <h2 class="main-text">
                        We excel in web development and can build you any size web application in your prefered framework.    
                    </h2>
                    <h3 class="main-text">
                        Tell us what your web needs are and how you'd like it built, and that's what we'll do. 
                    </h3>
                </div>

                <!-- Standalone Software -->
                <div class="mt-5 main-text-container container">
                    <h1 class="mokoto main-text title">App Development</span></h1>
                    <h2 class="main-text">
                        Need a GUI to interact with your web API, or a CLI to expedite data processing? We would be ecstatic to create either for you.
                    </h2>
                    <h3 class="main-text">
                        Tell us what your workflow is missing and we'll fill the gaps.
                    </h3>
                </div>

                <!-- Software Support -->
                <div class="mt-5 main-text-container container">
                    <h1 class="mokoto main-text title">Development Support</span></h1>
                    <h2 class="main-text">
                        Already have a software project? Need some help moving it to the next level? Need help with CI/CD? We can help with it all.
                    </h2>
                    <h3 class="main-text">
                        Our experts are raring and ready to support anything you can throw at them.
                    </h3>
                </div>

                <!-- Miscellaneous -->
                <div class="mt-4 main-text-container container">
                    <h2 class="main-text">
                        The categories above aren't quite what your looking for?
                    </h2>
                    <h3 class="main-text">
                        Send us a <a href="/contact" class="highlight">message</a> and let us know what you need.
                    </h3>
                </div>

                <!-- Call to action -->
                <hr style="margin-left: 30%; margin-right:30%; width: 40%;"/>
                <h1 class="text-center fs-1 mokoto">It all starts here</h1>
            </div>
            <%view mainfooter%>
        </main>
    </body>
</html>
